data.title: Elliot Page Shows Off a Duotone Suit, Plus Snoop Dogg, Serena Williams, Blake Lively and More
authors: Brian Anthony Hernandez, Escher Walcott, Brendan Le, Vic Verbalaitis, Stephanie Sengwe, Luke Chinman
data.meta_description: From Hollywood to New York and everywhere in between, see what your favorite stars are up to
data.text:
From Hollywood to New York and everywhere in between, see what your favorite stars are up to

Stars have been everywhere this week, from Snoop Dogg rapping for an Olympic audience in Paris to Elliot Page showing off a duotone suit at the premiere of The Umbrella Academy season 4 in Los Angeles. Over in New York City, Blake Lively flashed her signature smile while out on the town and Kit Harington stunned at the premiere of Industry season 3.

Here, are the best photos of celebs out and about this week. Come back tomorrow for more of the latest A-list outings!
